name: Sarah Carey
text: Good customer service Blaze....pizza was amazing alongside eating outdoors.  Drawback was outside bugs :-( other than all veggie toppings (literally), extra sauce with few slices of both pepperoni & Italian sausage. Young workers I found a little chatty but consistent. Try "create your own" soon with beer!!

text: Fast service and good pizza. The employees are friendly and do a good job assembling and making the pizzas. I’ve been to several blaze pizzas and this one is among my favorite.

name: Lortiko Varia
text: First time customer. Very solid pizza, good choices and flavors. Went with the build your own, many choices. Great way to try something different. Crust was perfect, overall very impressed. I will return and sample the other selections. Give it a shot.

name: Paul Richards
text: This place is worth a try. They serve large portions for fair rates. Regularly neat and with awesome mood. Would recommend to others.

text: I'm going to give it 3 stars for the time being. This is very similar to mod pizza but you are more limited on toppings at blaze. …More
